{"tid":2151419,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"中國玩家誇區投訴《赤毒》  反遭「遣返」回 中國 Steam","createTime":"2020-08-11T11:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T12:33:56.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b69f39f64b2576a57dc34b20c6e16de422236e0","tid":2151419,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Steam-01-1280x719.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2FSteam-01-1280x719.png&h=259f6d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣獨立開發者 Leonard H 製作的遊戲《赤毒》（Red Virus）以政治惡搞為主要內容，一推出即成功帶來噱頭，但也同樣引來中國玩家的檢舉。有一名中國玩家就在跨到俄羅斯區的狀態下，試圖向客服檢舉該遊戲，豈料反被「遣返」回 Steam 中國區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「赤毒」在各國爆發襲捲全世界為背景，講述無數中毒的 NMSLese 入侵自由世界赤化大地河流，將美國改造成 NMSLand，新鮮的題材令遊戲獲得不少用戶讚賞，但也同樣引來不少中國玩家的不滿。有一名中國玩家向 Steam 客服檢舉該遊戲，但卻因為自身誇區至俄羅斯區，故其投訴不被受理，還被引導回 Steam 中國區，以致其在俄羅斯區購買的遊戲全部作廢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/789aed5b86f8644ab75360734e9c1e4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F789aed5b86f8644ab75360734e9c1e4d.jpg&h=7b0da535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該名中國玩家以簡體中文向容客服投訴《赤毒》，指其違反了中國的法律，要求 Steam 將該遊戲下架。不過，客服卻以英文回信，指若對方認為遊戲屬犯了中國法律，應該向中國的 Steam 客服舉報，更「好心」將其帳號轉回中國區，以便他作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該名中國玩家其後到百度貼吧發布帖文求助，卻因為以簡體中文寫信一事而被其他中國網民嘲笑，指其行為高調愚蠢、「此地無銀三百兩」，似乎未能成功得到同胞們的安慰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/d931fa60-dad2-11ea-b7ff-114e04565a9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fd931fa60-dad2-11ea-b7ff-114e04565a9f.png&h=c48e9f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而不少台灣網民亦在討論區指，遊戲明明沒有在中國當地 Steam 上架，基本上中國玩家都無法以合法途徑入手該遊戲，而違法誇區的中國玩家竟想到在他區投訴該遊戲，也是相當「出色」，同時希望中國版「蒸氣平台」能夠快點上架，以讓中國玩家可以在所屬的遊戲區內暢玩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-08-11-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%886.40.26-1119x900.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-08-11-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25886.40.26-1119x900.png&h=d6bb43c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-08-11-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%886.40.38-988x900.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-08-11-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25886.40.38-988x900.png&h=b6fd7943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-08-11-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%886.25.17-1280x688.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-08-11-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25886.25.17-1280x688.png&h=994777ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/11/red-virus/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR1UNTRO-sguJDMETTiXvRRMU9AV2zEwXJmScGKh-ETPBU3wxOUPKVsAFZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F11%2Fred-virus%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1UNTRO-sguJDMETTiXvRRMU9AV2zEwXJmScGKh-ETPBU3wxOUPKVsAFZg&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=e9e3828b\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/11/red-virus/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR1UNTRO-sguJDMETTiXvRRMU9AV2zEwXJmScGKh-ETPBU3wxOUPKVsAFZg</a>"},{"pid":"a3e2f979ce9c77164317a8648620c7c72f035c6b","tid":2151419,"uid":55043,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"steam集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"